The opposite of [[Stress (psychology)|stressful]] is '''relaxed'''. It can refer to a situation, someone's character, or someone's [[mood]]. [[Cannabis]] and [[tranquilizer]]s may make somebody more relaxed.

An activity or lack of activity that makes one relaxed is called '''relaxing''' or [[leisure]].

Relaxing a rule is making it less strict.

